      • byTestingItemsWith

        public Multi<T> byTestingItemsWith(Function<? super T,? extends Uni<Boolean>> tester)
        Produces a Multi containing the items from this Multi passing the tester asynchronous test. Unlike byFilteringItemsWith(Predicate), the test is asynchronous. Note that this method preserves ordering of the items, even if the test is asynchronous.
        Parameters:
        tester - the predicate, must not be null, must not produce null
        Returns:
        the produced Multi
